"title": "8331: reliability",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8331: reliability",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of consistency and dependability which is the basis for confidence and reliance. It is exemplified by God in his changelessness and is required of God's people in their service and witness. Scripture gives warning, too, of those things which may prove unreliable.</p>\n<h2>The reliability of God</h2>\n<h3>God's character and nature are reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:7\">PSA 62:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:35\">PSA 78:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a></p>\n<h3>God is faithful to his covenants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:15-Gen9:16\">GEN 9:15–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:8-Ps105:11\">PSA 105:8–105:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:5\">PSA 111:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:60\">EZK 16:60</a></p>\n<h3>God's love is reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:1-Ps89:2\">PSA 89:1–89:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:6\">EXO 20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:10\">DEU 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18\">NUM 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:17-Ps103:18\">PSA 103:17–103:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22-Lam3:24\">LAM 3:22–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:16\">1JN 4:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's promises are reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:44-Josh21:45\">JOS 21:44–21:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:15\">JOS 23:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10\">JER 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:13-Heb6:18\">HEB 6:13–6:18</a></p>\n<h3>God's presence is reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:6\">DEU 31:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:15\">GEN 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:10\">ACT 18:10</a></p>\n<h3>God's strength and protection are reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:1\">PSA 46:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:8-1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:9\">JOS 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:18\">2CH 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:8\">2CH 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5-Ps71:7\">PSA 71:5–71:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>God's words are reliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:26\">JHN 8:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:25\">EZK 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:33\">LUK 21:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:4\">ROM 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>The reliability of times and seasons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:14\">GEN 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:19\">PSA 104:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:4-Eccl1:5\">ECC 1:4–1:5</a></p>\n<h2>The reliability of God's people</h2>\n<h3>Reliability in witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:2\">ISA 8:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:17\">PRO 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">PRO 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:25\">PRO 14:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:35\">JHN 19:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a></p>\n<h3>Reliability in teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:20-Prov22:21\">PRO 22:20–22:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:10\">ECC 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:2\">2TI 2:2</a></p>\n<h3>Reliability of character</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2-1Tim3:10\">1TI 3:2–3:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:6-Titus1:9\">TIT 1:6–1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of reliable people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:23-Gen21:24\">GEN 21:23–21:24</a> <em>Abraham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7\">NUM 12:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:5\">HEB 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:24\">NUM 14:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:9-Josh14:12\">JOS 14:9–14:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:12\">2CH 34:12</a> <em>men working on the temple</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:2\">NEH 7:2</a> <em>Hanani</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:15\">EZK 44:15</a> <em>Priests</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:6\">MAL 2:6</a> <em>Levi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:17\">1CO 4:17</a> <em>Timothy</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:7\">COL 1:7</a> <em>Epaphras</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7-Col4:9\">COL 4:7–4:9</a> <em>Tychicus and Onesimus</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:11\">2TI 4:11</a> <em>Luke</em></p>\n<h2>Warnings against unreliability</h2>\n<h3>Examples of unreliable people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:57\">PSA 78:57</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam29:6\">1SA 29:6</a> <em>David was trusted by Achish, but was secretly deceiving him</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:21\">JER 2:21</a> <em>the people of Israel</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:9\">EZK 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">MAT 7:15</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:4\">GAL 2:4</a> <em>Judaisers</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:4\">HOS 10:4</a> <em>Israel's kings</em></p>\n<h3>Examples of things proving unreliable</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5\">JER 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:21\">2KI 18:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:6\">ISA 36:6</a> <em>false dependence upon Egypt</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:16\">PSA 33:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:13\">HOS 10:13</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:12-Isa30:13\">ISA 30:12–30:13</a> <em>false dependence upon human scheming</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:18\">GAL 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a></p>",
